== Haggai achem Pustok ==
'''Book of Haggai'''


Hea pustokant lhan-lhan xittkavnnio asat.  Babilonient thaun portolole poile Judev Dev-mondir bandunk sodtat, tanchi humed moddtat.  Magir Hag’gai ani Zakaria he donui provadi tankam novo nett ditat ani Jerubbabel, Judachea razpalak toxench porom’ Iadnik Joshuak, Dev-mondir bandpacho vaur suru korunk vinonti kortat.  Hea vixim hea pustokant vachunk mellta.

Jedha Mondir ghorttan zaun aslem tedna Sorvespor xetkaranche koxtt nirfoll korta.  Jedna te Mondir bandunk suru kortat tedna Sorvespor tankam udorgot bhasaita.

Hem novem Mondir adlea poros odik porzolltolem: ani Jerubbabelak Devan venchun kaddun taka soglli podvi bhasailea.

